description: The Camco Stabilizer Jack Support is an 7-inch tall leveler that is great for use with stabilizer jacks that don't reach the ground. It can also be used with tongue jacks equipped with a footpad, or as a step stool if not otherwise in use. The Stabilizer Jack Support is constructed of durable UV-stabilized polypropylene, and nests for storage if you own more than one.
